{"tid":730271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5年加1600月薪 咁都算顯著增長?","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T13:00:52.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56d10f0976121efd22b35b3ec060f0c6700ad947","tid":730271,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"今日有新聞報道政府最新數據，話年輕畢業生工資顯著增長，講到年輕一代會有上流機會；之但係百物騰貴，唔少今日仲喺中環打拼嘅年輕人，相信對所謂「實質月薪」都會有唔少異議。<br />\n<br />\n統計處數據顯示，20至29歲從事全職工作的年輕人，實質月薪中位數，由2013年嘅13400元增加至15000元，而30至39歲嘅80後，就由18400元上升到20000元。<br />\n<br />\n詳細數據如下：<br />\n<br />\n20歲以下 ：9200元升至10,200元 增加11%<br />\n20至29歲 ：13,400元升至15,000元 增加12%<br />\n30至39歲 ：18,400元升至20,000元 增加8.7%<br />\n40至49歲 ：19,000元升至20,000元 增加5.3%<br />\n50至59歲 ：15,500元升至18,000元 增加16.1%<br />\n60至69歲 ：11,200元升至13,000元 增加16.07%<br />\n70歲及以上：10,100元升至10,000元 增加1%<br />\n表面睇，年輕人加人工係好事，80後實質月薪中位數，亦終於達到兩萬元，如此一來，人活到30歲，都至少要有兩皮人工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pAemhZTj.7aLfzK07hcnGg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/659c87788562ebfcc46704ff342f7939\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpAemhZTj.7aLfzK07hcnGg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F659c87788562ebfcc46704ff342f7939&h=1e313aa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69232d33f38e67f4cc9f798d3835cc295d7ab344","tid":730271,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR，你係咪仲做緊地盤呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba38dcbcdef615322039a3444f0b43803348f5b6","tid":730271,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb12b7c9a2fd71a0e711812b9260dc85d4e87f5d","tid":730271,"uid":71740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"70歲及以上：10,100元升至10,000元 增加1%<br />\n？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？"},{"pid":"ec5740c125bdb49d381f60a32ea5ab8a0d2a304b","tid":730271,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"點解全部得萬幾？"},{"pid":"e41dc06b2248fe2ef8400923e278868c4fb89cc7","tid":730271,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"根本個數就唔準"},{"pid":"3de36ed38829c4002a1f506a245bfaa3ad1afbfa","tid":730271,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"實際收入係唔到統計中位數嘅一半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123ce9ca57b7949e8c72c100b0ba780879e2a854","tid":730271,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"專材呢？"},{"pid":"71f743abae93c3baf202024202aefbd94ce4454f","tid":730271,"uid":60765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"2013年到2018年，5年時間加左1k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3348150a8635ac6331e7b086b2146d56a5b7e509","tid":730271,"uid":60765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2013年到2018年，5年時間加左1.6k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1a0bf5f5844b0c9ac129ab8f3c60dd6c5de83a2","tid":730271,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"樂觀咁諗 有糧出已經算好"},{"pid":"9579e01b437ffe30fdda632ce6d343675c16edd3","tid":730271,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"我一向貼錢返工為咗學野，<br />\n五年先貼多千幾一個月我覺得好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0893b0393a3ce13ac5c71bfd7c30053cbf694678","tid":730271,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"樓